node.title: One injured after Blockhouse Bay firearms incident
node.description: Neighbours reported hearing loud bangs at the Auckland address at about 1.15pm.
node.content:
["Police have cordoned off an address in Blockhouse Bay, Auckland, after a firearms incident.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Marika Khabazi\n
", "Neighbours reported hearing loud bangs at the Exminster Street address at about 1.15pm.", "Police say shortly after a man turned up at an Avondale medical centre with injuries to his leg.", "He was taken to hospital.", "No arrests have been made and enquiries are ongoing, police said."]
